{"content":[{"key":"header","data":{"content":"极客编辑器 GeekEditor 新手教程","level":1},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<strong>极客编辑器</strong>是一款所见即所得（WYSIWYG）富文本沉浸式写作排版编辑器，它注重高效创作，可多开文档编辑，同时支持Markdown语法输入及一键排版。<br>它注重内容隐私及数据安全，目前已支持本地、GitHub、GitLab及Gitee仓库文档存储，支持无图床插入图片，同时支持配置独立GitHub、GitLab仓库作为图床。<br>当前，编辑器除了支持常用内容块外，并支持了代码块、LaTex数学公式、Mermaid图表、Drawio制图，可以<strong>一键复制/同步到微信公众号、知乎及掘金</strong>等平台发布。<br>此外，编辑器支持了截图粘贴以及本地图片文件拖拽至编辑区任意位置等便捷功能，以及支持<strong>导出图片、Word、PDF、HTML及Markdown</strong>等格式文件。<br><strong>在线版</strong>：<a href=\"https://www.geekeditor.com/\">https://www.geekeditor.com</a><br><strong>桌面软件历史版本</strong>：<a href=\"https://github.com/geekeditor/geekeditor-releases/releases\">https://github.com/geekeditor/geekeditor-releases/releases</a><br><strong>浏览器插件</strong>：开发中"},"common":{"quote":true}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"历史版本记录：<a href=\"https://github.com/geekeditor/geekeditor-releases/blob/main/versions.md\">https://github.com/geekeditor/geekeditor-releases/blob/main/versions.md</a><br>Issues：<a href=\"https://github.com/geekeditor/geekeditor-releases/issues\">https://github.com/geekeditor/geekeditor-releases/issues</a>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"功能特征","level":2},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">行内格式</strong>：<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">加粗</strong>、斜体、<u>下划线</u>、<del>删除线</del>、<a href=\"https://www.geekeditor.com\">超链接</a>、<mark>高亮</mark>、<code>行内代码</code>、<kbd style=\"padding: 2px 4px; font: 75% Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, Courier, monospace; line-height: 1; color: #5f6368; vertical-align: middle; background-color: #f3f3f3; border: solid 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\">键盘文本</kbd>、<sup>上标</sup>、<sub>下标</sub>、<span>字号</span>、<span>颜色</span>、<span>背景色</span>、数学公式、<footnote data-note=\"示例注释\" data-title=\"\">脚注<span>[1]</span></footnote>、〖快捷括号〗，均支持快捷键操作<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">标题</strong>：1~6级标题<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">图片</strong>：上传至GitHub/GitLab仓库，支持设置标题，支持图片编辑美化，支持拖拽本地图片文件到编辑区（可自由选择位置），支持粘贴其它软件截图<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">有序列表/无序列表</strong>：支持两者之间的快捷转换<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">待办事项</strong>：支持与有序列表/无序列表之间转换<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">表格</strong>：支持表格行列快捷新增及删除<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">代码块</strong>：支持常见代码语言自动识别及高亮显示<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">分割线</strong><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">数学公式</strong>：支持Tex行内公式及块公式快捷编写<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Mermaid 图表</strong>：支持Mermaid语法编写<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Drawio 制图</strong>：内置了Drawio制图工具，支持流程图、UML等制图<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">脚注</strong>：文中设置脚注后，可在文尾部添加脚注块呈现<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">主题排版</strong>：内置5个主题，并支持自定义编写主题风格<strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">发布</strong>：支持复制发布到微信公众号、知乎、掘金平台，支持复制为HTML、Markdown及纯文本"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"基本操作","level":2},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"<strong>插入内容块</strong>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[{"content":"后增新的文字内容块：移动光标到目标内容块，按Enter键","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"同一个文字内容块中新增段落/空行：移动光标到目标位置后，按Shift+Enter键","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"新增其它内容块","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[{"content":"在空行，按Tab键弹出工具栏，按左、右方向键(←/→键)选择要新增类型，按Enter键(或鼠标点击操作)新建","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"在空行，输入Markdown语法，按Space(或Enter)键新建","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]}]},{"content":"<strong>插入行内数学公式</strong><strong>：</strong>在光标处，按Insert键弹出数学公式编写框","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<strong>行内文字格式化</strong>：","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[{"content":"选中文字，将弹出工具栏，按左、右方向键(←/→键)选择要格式化的类型，按Enter键(或鼠标点击操作)确认","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"按上、下方向键(↑↓)或Esc键，取消文字选中及隐藏工具栏","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"快捷键操作，请点击编辑器右上角•••按钮查看","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},{"content":"<strong>编辑图片/公式/图表/Drawio:</strong>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[{"content":"鼠标双击","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"选中后，按Command/Ctrl + Enter键","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]}]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"Markdown语法","level":2},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"ordered","items":[{"content":"<strong>标题</strong>（<code>#~#######</code>：一级~六级标题）","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[{"content":"空二级标题：<code>##</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"带内容二级标题：<code>##标题</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},{"content":"<strong>图片</strong>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[{"content":"空图片内容块：<code>！</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"标题不为空的图片内容块：<code>!(标题)</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"标题及图片都不为空的图片内容块：<code>!(标题)[https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/montisan/imagehosting/geekeditor_images/2021-7-12/1626067390603-qrcode_for_geekeditor.jpg]</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},{"content":"<strong>列表</strong>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[{"content":"有序列表：<code>1.</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"无序列表：<code>-</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},{"content":"<strong>待办事项</strong>：<code>-[]</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<strong>分割线</strong>：<code>---</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<strong>表格</strong>：<code>||</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<strong>数学公式</strong>：<code>$$</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<strong>代码块</strong>：<code>```</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<strong>Mermaid图表</strong>：<code>`mermaid</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<strong>Drawio制图</strong>：<code>`drawio</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"<strong>脚注</strong>：<code>`footnote</code><code>Space/Enter键</code>","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"个人数据","level":2},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"所有的文档数据都保存在本地或者个人仓库(GitHub/Gitee等)，当前编辑器不云存储任何数据。","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"数据存储使用了JSON纯文本格式，支持复制、导出图片、Word、PDF、HTML、Markdown等格式文件。","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"仓库存储","level":2},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<strong>示例文档</strong>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"如您所见，打开编辑器时，默认内置了一个的示例文档。您可以在示例文档进行初步操作体验。<mark>提示</mark>：<strong>因示例文档配置的GitHub图床AccessToken总被人恶意清除，示例文档中不能演示图片上传。请您配置个人独立的文档仓库及图床后再进行写作。示例文档可以在设置中隐藏</strong>。"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"注：示例文档中默认内置的文档，如被修改，将在页面刷新后被重置。"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<strong>配置仓库</strong>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"在左下角“设置”中可以配置存储仓库，新添加时，需要配置两个仓库：一个文档存储仓库，一个文档对应的图床仓库。目前，仓库支持本地、GitHub、GitLab（国内推荐）以及Gitee。<code>文档仓库可设置公开或私有仓库，建议使用私有仓库；图床必须使用公开仓库</code>。GitHub、GitLab及Gitee均使用Access Token的方式存取，因此，需要您注册好GitHub/GitLab/Gitee账户，并在平台设置里创建好可以访问仓库的AccessToken。"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU3MDMyNDk5OQ==&amp;mid=2247484407&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ab0f37ce346bc4f3bc9ca4a9544fa0e9&amp;chksm=fcf0629fcb87eb890a3939b2d9579bdb1bd6a14cc234bca37c9b799f59090031bbd316aea341&amp;token=1201531960&amp;lang=zh_CN#rd\">如何创建GitHub仓库及生成获取AccessToken？</a><span>（👈&nbsp; 按住Command/Win键，点击鼠标打开）</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU3MDMyNDk5OQ==&amp;mid=2247484534&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ce394638528a92f3bc581f7d08f74e99&amp;chksm=fcf0651ecb87ec08102d798394d6ace942595257378727dc3b0a2eca3c3b546997e2242c93f2#wechat_redirect\">如何创建GitLab仓库及生成获取AccessToken？</a><span>（👈&nbsp; 按住Command/Win键，点击鼠标打开）</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU3MDMyNDk5OQ==&amp;mid=2247484407&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=001a4a6ac7b3bd26442286672a4b1a9f&amp;chksm=fcf0629fcb87eb89a8381c43389237ba4ce76a68127c69728dcc0cb5df12f5f12765af7523f8&amp;token=1201531960&amp;lang=zh_CN#rd\">如何创建Gitee仓库及生成获取AccessToken？</a><span>（👈&nbsp; 按住Command/Win键，点击鼠标打开）</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<strong>注意事项</strong>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"配置GitHub/GitLab/Gitee仓库时，<code>请按教程操作确保仓库已初始化</code>。Gitee新创建仓库时，初始化选项默认是非选中状态，请在创建仓库的时候选中初始化仓库。"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"header","data":{"content":"Reference","level":3},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>[ 1 ] </span><span>示例注释</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":""},"common":{}}],"typeset":"typeset-1687836132043","layout":"print","basic":{"title":"","cover":"","summary":""}}